\pard\f0\fs28 Subsp.{\b  brevipes} (Tausch) Wulf,{\i  Fl. Kryma }{\b 1:} 20 (1927), with tough, stiff, pale-green petioles, coriaceous lamina, thickly lanate beneath, few pinnae, and with croziers lacking red hairs, has been described from Kriti and Krym. Its identity is uncertain.
