\pard\f0\fs28 Rhizome ascending. Leaves 1-pinnate, with deeply pinnatisect pinnae and abundant yellow glands beneath; veins free, reaching margin. Sori orbicular, near the margin of the segment; indusium caducous; spores winged, with raised reticulum.
